snippet.title: Bayonetta Origins: Cereza and the Lost Demon — Announcement Trailer — Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Turn back the pages of the Umbra Witch's story to learn where it all began. Take control of Cereza and her first demon Cheshire to fend off faeries and solve puzzles when Bayonetta Origins: Cereza and the Lost Demon releases March 17, 2023 only on Nintendo Switch. Pre-orders are now available!
